(473, '\n				Silver was &amp;apos;moved&amp;apos; by LeBron&amp;apos;s statement\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/15/silver-on-lebron.ap/index.html?rss=true\n			', 'LeBron James'' decision to return to play for the Cleveland Cavaliers, and the eloquent essay in Sports Illustrated that outlined the lure of home, resonated with many who watched the saga unfold last week.', 3, 1405483525, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 00:05:25 EDT', 0),
