(501, 'Islanders agree to deals with C Cizikas, D de Haan', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726299', '\r\nUNIONDALE, N.Y. - The New York Islanders agreed to terms with centre Casey Cizikas and defenceman Calvin de Haan on Tuesday.\r\n\r\nCizikas, 23, got a two-year contract. He scored six goals and 10 assists last season, his second full year with the c...', 4, 1405470901, 'Tue, 15 Jul 2014 20:35:01 EDT', 0),
(502, 'Detroit Red Wings hire Granato as assistant coach; Renney taking over Hockey Canada', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726298', '\r\nDETROIT - The Detroit Red Wings have hired Tony Granato as an assistant coach.\r\n\r\nGranato was an assistant for the Pittsburgh Penguins for the last five seasons, and he was also part of Team USA''s staff at the 2014 Olympics. Granato also has bee...', 4, 1405467304, 'Tue, 15 Jul 2014 19:35:04 EDT', 0),
