(505, 'Fried makes ''14 debut at Fort Wayne', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/padres-no-2-prospect-max-fried-makes-2014-debut-at-fort-wayne?ymd=20140717&content_id=84980660&vkey=news_mlb', 'Left-hander Max Fried, the Padres'' No. 2 prospect, made his first start of the year with a full-season club Wednesday. He threw 3 2/3 innings in Class A Fort Wayne''s 9-2 victory at Quad Cities.', 1, 1405571114, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 00:25:14 EDT\n	', 0),
(506, 'Top prospect Gray sharp for ninth Double-A win', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/colorado-rockies-top-prospect-jon-gray-sharp-for-ninth-win-with-tulsa?ymd=20140716&content_id=84975240&vkey=news_mlb', 'Rockies'' No. 1 prospect Jon Gray threw 5 2/3 scoreless innings Wednesday in Double-A Tulsa''s 2-0 victory. Gray, ranked No. 13 on MLBPipeline.com''s Top 100 Prospects list, allowed one hit and two walks, striking out seven.', 1, 1405569031, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 23:50:31 EDT\n	', 0),
(507, 'Moya named Eastern League ASG MVP', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/tigers-prospect-steven-moya-is-eastern-league-all-star-game-mvp?ymd=20140716&content_id=84970466&vkey=news_mlb', 'Outfielder Steven Moya, the Tigers'' No. 20 prospect, hit a grand slam and was named MVP of the Eastern League All-Star Game on Wednesday. His blast helped the Western Division defeat the Eastern Division, 5-2.', 1, 1405565501, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 22:51:41 EDT\n	', 0),
(508, 'Twins'' top prospect Buxton busts out with three hits', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/top-prospect-byron-buxton-busts-out-with-three-hits-at-fort-myers?ymd=20140716&content_id=84968446&vkey=news_mlb', 'Twins farmhand Byron Buxton, baseball''s top prospect, collected three hits Wednesday, helping Class A Advanced Fort Myers defeat Daytona, 5-1. Outfielder Adam Brett Walker II, the Twins'' No. 12 prospect, leads the Florida State League with 20 homers.', 1, 1405564201, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 22:30:01 EDT\n	', 0),
(509, 'Setback pushes Dirks'' return to Tigers to unknown date', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/setback-pushes-andy-dirks-return-to-unknown-date?ymd=20140716&content_id=84955210&vkey=news_mlb', 'After a week of game action, Andy Dirks'' comeback from back surgery has hit a snag. The Tigers announced Wednesday that they''ve recalled Dirks from his rehab assignment with Class A Lakeland, and will keep him on the disabled list.', 1, 1405562799, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 22:06:39 EDT\n	', 0),
(510, 'Statcast offers in-depth look at All-Star highlights', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/statcast-tracking-technology-offers-in-depth-look-at-all-star-highlights?ymd=20140716&content_id=84947898&vkey=news_mlb', 'From the raw power of Giancarlo Stanton in Monday''s Home Run Derby to the speed-power combination of MVP Mike Trout and the baserunning acumen of Derek Jeter in the All-Star Game, Statcast technology highlights some of what made the festivities so much fun.', 1, 1405551026, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 18:50:26 EDT\n	', 0),
(511, 'Putting Bumgarner''s bat in perspective', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/marty-noble-putting-madison-bumgarner-in-perspective?ymd=20140716&content_id=84946680&vkey=news_mlb', 'Just a second. What is the big fuss about Madison Bumgarner? So he''s hit three home runs this season, and two of them have been grand slams. Nice, but before we re-involve ourselves in the pennant races, please allow for a repeat of the question and some explanation of why hitting three home runs, two of them slams, in a season doesn''t seem like all that much to folks who monitored the game before last week.', 1, 1405569639, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 00:00:39 EDT\n	', 0),
(512, 'Gattis will move rehab to Triple-A on Thursday', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/gattis-will-move-rehab-to-triple-a-on-thursday?ymd=20140716&content_id=84936586&vkey=news_mlb', 'Braves catcher Evan Gattis, who has been sidelined by a bulging disc in his back since late June, will ,move his rehab assignment from Class A Rome to Triple-A Gwinnett on Thursday.', 1, 1405539312, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 15:35:12 EDT\n	', 0),
(513, 'Ruiz could return to lineup next week', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/philadelphia-phillies-catcher-carlos-ruiz-is-set-for-a-rehab-assignment-and-could-return-as-early-as-next-week?ymd=20140716&content_id=84933220&vkey=news_mlb', 'Carlos Ruiz, on the DL since June 27 with a concussion, will begin a rehab assignment Thursday and could return to the lineup next week.', 1, 1405535575, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 14:32:55 EDT\n	', 0),
(514, 'Nats look to build on momentum coming out of break', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/nationals-look-to-build-on-momentum-coming-out-of-break?ymd=20140716&content_id=84871192&vkey=news_mlb', 'Before the 2014 season started, the Nationals were heavily favored to win the National League East. The first half started slowly, but the Nationals were able to turn it around and ended the first half with a 51-42 record and in a first-place tie with the Braves in the division.', 1, 1405533638, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 14:00:38 EDT\n	', 0),
