(549, 'Cahill set for return after more than a month in Minors', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140717&content_id=85044294&notebook_id=85044296&vkey=notebook_ari&c_id=ari', 'Trevor Cahill hasn''t played a Major League game in more than a month. But he will get a second chance when he gets the ball against the Cubs on Friday night at Chase Field.', 1, 1405645692, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 21:08:12 EDT\n	', 0),
