(678, '\n				Randle prepares to join a crowded frontcourt in L.A.\n				', 'http://www.nba.com/2014/news/07/18/rookie-ladder-after-day-7/index.html?rss=true\n			', 'Neither the departure of Pau Gasol nor the arrival of Ed Davis were expected to affect Julius Randle and the start of his NBA career that much. Not when Gasol''s departure could be seen coming from months away whether the Lakers added a replacement power forward in the draft or not and Davis signing for the minimum as a free agent indicated the level of belief around the league he is capable of holding down big minutes.', 3, 1405686211, 'Fri, 18 Jul 2014 08:23:31 EDT', 0),
(679, 'White Sox to take stage at Wild Pitches fundraiser', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/cws/white-sox-to-take-stage-at-wild-pitches-fundraiser?ymd=20140717&content_id=85012480&vkey=news_cws', 'White Sox players will be showing off their talents and humor at the second annual Wild Pitches, a charity event held at Bub City on Sunday evening, July 20, to raise money for White Sox Charities and the Ronald McDonald House Charities of Chicagoland and Northwest Indiana.', 1, 1405623082, 'Thu, 17 Jul 2014 14:51:22 EDT\n	', 6),
(680, 'Alexei replaces legend, part of AL''s game-winning rally', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/cws/white-sox-shortstop-alexei-ramirez-replaces-derek-jeter-part-of-als-rally?ymd=20140716&content_id=84822490&vkey=news_cws', 'White Sox shortstop Alexei Ramirez took the reins from Derek Jeter in the fourth inning of Tuesday night''s All-Star Game and then helped the American League stake a claim to home-field advantage in the World Series with a 5-3 victory at Target Field.', 1, 1405490219, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:56:59 EDT\n	', 6),
(681, 'AL-Americans: Jeter, Trout spark victory', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_15_nasmlb_aasmlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=al', 'Mike Trout delivered the go-ahead hit and the game''s first run, winning the All-Star MVP Award, but it was Derek Jeter who stole the show in his final Midsummer Classic. Jeter went 2-for-2 with a run scored to set the tone for the AL, which won home-field advantage in the World Series.', 1, 1405487657, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 01:14:17 EDT\n	', 6);
