(682, 'Young talent to continue to lead Sox in second half', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/cws/young-talent-to-continue-to-lead-white-sox-in-second-half?ymd=20140715&content_id=84790128&vkey=news_cws', 'While the season has not gone as planned so far, it''s certainly a considerable step in the right direction for the White Sox behind Jose Abreu, Chris Sale, Jose Quintana and Adam Eaton, to name a few, as they prepare for the second half.', 1, 1405535824, 'Wed, 16 Jul 2014 14:37:04 EDT\n	', 6),
(683, 'Dodgers activate Beckett, option Rodriguez', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/dodgers-activate-beckett-option-rodriguez?ymd=20140722&content_id=85736364&vkey=news_mlb', 'Dodgers reliever Paco Rodriguez was optioned back to Triple-A Albuquerque to make room for the activation of Tuesday night''s starting pitcher Josh Beckett.', 1, 1406059982, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 16:13:02 EDT\n	', 0),
(684, 'Barney designated as Bonifacio, Hendricks return', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/cubs-emilio-bonifacio-kyle-hendricks-return-darwin-barney-designated?ymd=20140722&content_id=85734422&vkey=news_mlb', 'The Cubs designated 2012 Gold Glove second baseman Darwin Barney for assignment on Tuesday to make room on the roster for Emilio Bonifacio, who was activated from the disabled list. They also optioned left-hander Zac Rosscup to Triple-A Iowa and recalled right-hander Kyle Hendricks.', 1, 1406057808, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 15:36:48 EDT\n	', 0),
(685, 'A''s activate Reddick from 15-day DL', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/as-activate-outfielder-josh-reddick-from-15-day-dl?ymd=20140722&content_id=85734654&vkey=news_mlb', 'The A''s reinstated outfielder Josh Reddick from the 15-day disabled list, the club announced today. The A''s also announced that infielder Andy Parrino was optioned to Triple-A Sacramento following the game Sunday.', 1, 1406057709, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 15:35:09 EDT\n	', 0),
(686, 'Yanks buy low on Headley, but will bat recover?', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/anthony-castrovince-yankees-buy-low-on-slugger-chase-headley-but-will-his-bat-recover?ymd=20140722&content_id=85733584&vkey=news_mlb', 'Once the face of the Padres, Chase Headley was sent to the Yankees for much smaller return than he once could have landed for the Friars. And while the Yankees hope his offensive levels return to its prior form, his glove will play at New York''s hot corner.', 1, 1406055021, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 14:50:21 EDT\n	', 0),
(687, 'Yanks get everyday third baseman in Headley', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/yankees-acquire-chase-headley-from-padres?ymd=20140722&content_id=85731608&vkey=news_mlb', 'Residing within striking distance in the American League East, the Yankees sent a clear message on Tuesday that they intend to push for the postseason, completing a trade with the Padres for third baseman Chase Headley.', 1, 1406052306, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 14:05:06 EDT\n	', 0),
(688, 'Garagiola''s life full of achievements and giving', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/richard-justice-joe-garagiolas-life-full-of-achievements?ymd=20140722&content_id=85723304&vkey=news_mlb', 'Joe Garagiola''s wonderful life has been one of humor and giving, of dignity, integrity and grace. Baseball has been a constant -- his enduring love. Yet that''s just part of the story. Rather than curse the darkness, he has lit candles, hundreds of them.', 1, 1406043331, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 11:35:31 EDT\n	', 0),
(689, 'Top prospect Sanchez promoted by Blue Jays', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/blue-jays-call-up-top-pitching-prospect-aaron-sanchez?ymd=20140722&content_id=85720748&vkey=news_mlb', 'The Blue Jays called up their top prospect, right-hander Aaron Sanchez, amid a flurry of roster moves Tuesday.', 1, 1406056803, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 15:20:03 EDT\n	', 0),
(690, 'Today''s MLB starting lineups: July 22', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/todays-mlb-starting-lineups-july-22?ymd=20140722&content_id=82355302&vkey=news_mlb', 'Every lineup, every day, as they are made public by the clubs.', 1, 1406054739, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 14:45:39 EDT\n	', 0),
(691, 'Ackley''s amazing heist a product of determination', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140721&content_id=85593872&notebook_id=85703644&vkey=notebook_sea&c_id=sea', 'Dustin Ackley has only been playing the outfield since midseason last year, but the former second baseman looked like a natural on Monday night as he went over the left-field wall at Safeco Field to rob the Mets'' Travis d''Arnaud of a home run in the sixth inning.', 1, 1406011590, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 02:46:30 EDT\n	', 0),
(692, 'Bargain bin: Ranking the top 10 offseason signings', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/scott-kazmir-and-nelson-cruz-are-among-baseballs-best-bargains-this-season?ymd=20140722&content_id=85702984&vkey=news_mlb', 'As soon as Koji Uehara recorded the final strikeout during last year''s World Series, it seemed teams were already busy jockeying for 2014 position in the free-agent market. With the benefit of some hindsight, here''s a list of the top 10 signings for the money.', 1, 1406010495, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 02:28:15 EDT\n	', 0),
