(768, 'First career save gives Lincecum rare feat', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/tim-lincecum-adds-first-career-save-to-no-hitter-in-same-season?ymd=20140723&content_id=85878556&vkey=news_mlb', 'With the Giants having exhausted their bullpen, in terms of manpower and energy, Tim Lincecum stepped forward to record the final two outs and earn his first Major League save in Tuesday night''s 9-6, 14-inning victory over the Philadelphia Phillies.', 1, 1406098021, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 02:47:01 EDT\n	', 0),
(769, 'Hoes'' homer lifts Astros in 12-inning showdown', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_22_houmlb_oakmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=hou', 'Outfielder L.J. Hoes, who was hitless in his first four at-bats, launched a solo homer to left field off relief pitcher Fernando Abad with one out in the 12th to send the Astros to their third consecutive win over the A''s, 3-2, at O.co Coliseum.', 1, 1406099892, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 03:18:12 EDT\n	', 0),
(770, 'Chen ties Mariano for Panamanian wins mark', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/royals-lefty-bruce-chen-matches-mariano-rivera-for-panamanian-wins-mark?ymd=20140723&content_id=85869652&vkey=news_mlb', 'Bruce Chen and Mariano Rivera now share something besides their homeland. Both of the longtime pitchers have 82 career victories, tying them for the most by a Panamanian-born player. Chen earned No. 82 in the Royals'' 7-1 win over the White Sox on Tuesday night.', 1, 1406094306, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 01:45:06 EDT\n	', 0),
(771, 'deGrom pads RoY resume in win over Mariners', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_22_nynmlb_seamlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=nym', 'Jacob deGrom, who is approaching an innings load that may cause the Mets to start tapering off the rookie righty''s use, delivered yet another solid outing in a 3-1 win over the Mariners on Tuesday night.', 1, 1406096241, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 02:17:21 EDT\n	', 0),
