(795, 'Kreider, Rangers agree to two-year contract: report', 'http://www.nhl.com/ice/news.htm?id=726960', 'Forward Chris Kreider and the New York Rangers avoided a salary arbitration hearing by agreeing Wednesday to a two-year contract worth nearly $5 million, according to multiple media reports. \r\n\r\nThe contract reportedly is worth $2.35 million for t...', 4, 1406123400, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 09:50:00 EDT', 0),
