(802, 'That''s one: Street gets first save for Angels', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/thats-one-huston-street-gets-first-save-for-angels?ymd=20140724&content_id=86055050&vkey=news_mlb', 'Huston Street doesn''t have a nameplate above his locker yet, but he does have his first save as an Angel.', 1, 1406182819, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 02:20:19 EDT\n	', 0),
(803, 'Angels have morphed into a monster team', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/richard-justice-angels-have-morphed-into-a-monster-team?ymd=20140724&content_id=86056060&vkey=news_mlb', 'The 60-40 Angels are a reminder that winning doesn''t happen overnight, even when the blueprint is smart and the execution flawless. They''re also a reminder that the best general managers find players here, there and everywhere.', 1, 1406181751, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 02:02:31 EDT\n	', 0),
(804, 'Late rally carries Halos over Orioles in finale', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_23_balmlb_anamlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=ana', 'Behind eight solid innings from Jered Weaver and two late runs, the Angels rallied to beat the Orioles, 3-2, on Wednesday night at Angel Stadium.', 1, 1406178325, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 01:05:25 EDT\n	', 0),
(805, 'Pence''s antics highlight Wacky Wednesday', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/hunter-pences-antics-highlight-wacky-wednesday?ymd=20140724&content_id=86051130&vkey=news_mlb', 'It was a Wacky Wednesday around the Majors. From mascot mouth-to-mouth resuscitation to cracker "home plate" delivery, it was quite an eventful day.', 1, 1406179817, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 01:30:17 EDT\n	', 0),
