(807, 'Jay strikes out as ump loses track of count', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/cardinals-jon-jay-strikes-out-as-ump-loses-track-of-count?ymd=20140724&content_id=86047272&vkey=news_mlb', 'In a perplexing seventh-inning sequence during Wednesday''s 3-0 loss to the Rays, Jon Jay took both ball four and strike three in the same plate appearance.', 1, 1406176493, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 00:34:53 EDT\n	', 0),
(808, 'Papelbon unconcerned by struggles, trades', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85921634&notebook_id=86045026&vkey=notebook_phi&c_id=phi', 'Jonathan Papelbon made it crystal clear he wants to be traded before the July 31 non-waiver Trade Deadline, but the past couple of games have not helped his cause.', 1, 1406175527, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 00:18:47 EDT\n	', 0),
(809, 'Roma blanks Liverpool in Fenway friendly', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/roma-blanks-liverpool-in-fenway-friendly?ymd=20140724&content_id=86043978&vkey=news_mlb', 'Even with the Red Sox in Toronto, the bars and streets surrounding Fenway Park had a normal feel to them on Wednesday night. Drinks flowed and the cheers were loud as fans dressed in red prepared to enter the stadium. That red was worn in support of Liverpool FC, which took on AS Roma in a friendly at a sold-out Fenway Park. Roma won, 1-0, scoring off a corner kick in the 89th minute.', 1, 1406174444, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 00:00:44 EDT\n	', 0),
(810, 'Rangers, Yanks derailed by unexpected deluge', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/rangers-yankees-derailed-by-unexpected-deluge?ymd=20140723&content_id=86031244&vkey=news_mlb', 'When the rain started pouring with one out in the bottom of the fifth inning at Yankee Stadium on Wednesday night, it came down much more abruptly and faster than anyone anticipated.', 1, 1406177739, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 00:55:39 EDT\n	', 0),
(811, 'Bumgarner, Pence star in Giants'' victory', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_23_sfnmlb_phimlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=sf', 'Known for their energy and durability, Hunter Pence and Madison Bumgarner looked ready Wednesday night to tow the Giants into October with their efforts in a 3-1 triumph over the Phillies.', 1, 1406177338, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 00:48:58 EDT\n	', 0),
