(894, 'Competitive Balance Lottery pays out 12 Draft picks', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/cle/competitive-balance-lottery-pays-out-12-draft-picks?ymd=20140723&content_id=85923640&vkey=news_cle', 'The order of the 2015 First-Year Player Draft began to take shape Wednesday when the Competitive Balance Lottery was held at the Commissioner''s Office in New York. This year, the Marlins won the lottery and will receive the first pick of Competitive Balance Round A, which is held immediately after the Draft''s first round. The Marlins will be followed by the Rockies, Cardinals, Brewers, Padres and Indians.', 1, 1406141278, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 14:47:58 EDT\n	', 7),
(895, 'Tribe hopes Kluber can keep rolling at The K', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_24_clemlb_kcamlb_1&mode=preview&vkey=preview_web_away&c_id=cle', 'The series opener between the division-rival Indians and Royals at Kauffman Stadium on Thursday will fittingly feature a clash between two quality arms, with Cleveland turning to right-hander Corey Kluber and Kansas City going with southpaw Danny Duffy.', 1, 1406154042, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 18:20:42 EDT\n	', 7),
(896, 'Bourn back to running as he rehabs left hamstring', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85902742&notebook_id=85910170&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle', 'The next step for Michael Bourn is running without pain in his left hamstring. Cleveland''s speedy outfielder has been out of commission since re-injuring the hammy on July 5, an ailment that forced him to have surgery last year and kept him out of games earlier this season.', 1, 1406131816, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 12:10:16 EDT\n	', 7),
(897, 'Masterson throws bullpen before last start in Minors', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85902742&notebook_id=85909818&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle', 'Justin Masterson''s short stay in Minnesota was simply to let him get a bullpen session in with pitching coach Mickey Callaway. Masterson will fly back to Columbus on Thursday and make one more start at the Triple-A level before the team decides he''s ready for Major League hitters.', 1, 1406131814, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 12:10:14 EDT\n	', 7),
(898, 'Indians recall infield prospect Ramirez, option House', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85902742&notebook_id=85904988&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle', 'The Indians on Wednesday recalled infielder Jose Ramirez from Triple-A Columbus and optioned rookie southpaw T.J. House to Columbus.', 1, 1406127699, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 11:01:39 EDT\n	', 7),
(899, 'Indians drop series despite Bauer''s quality start', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_23_clemlb_minmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=cle', 'Trevor Bauer allowed three runs over six innings, but Cleveland couldn''t reach Minnesota spot starter Anthony Swarzak in a 3-1 loss on Wednesday afternoon at Target Field.', 1, 1406152226, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 17:50:26 EDT\n	', 7),
(900, 'Lindor singles, scores in Triple-A debut', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/cle/cleveland-indians-prospect-francisco-lindor-singles-scores-in-triple-a-debut?ymd=20140723&content_id=85839502&vkey=news_cle', 'The Indians'' No. 1 prospect, Francisco Lindor, singled and scored a run on Tuesday in his first game since being promoted to Triple-A Columbus. He helped Columbus defeat Louisville, 8-5.', 1, 1406088374, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 00:06:14 EDT\n	', 7),
(901, 'Santana collects four hits in Indians'' rout of Twins', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_22_clemlb_minmlb_1&mode=recap_away&c_id=cle', 'Carlos Santana went 4-for-5 with a homer and two RBIs during the Indians'' 8-2 win against the Twins on Tuesday night at Target Field.', 1, 1406092582, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 01:16:22 EDT\n	', 7),
(902, 'Indians option Lee to Triple-A Columbus', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140722&content_id=85772392&notebook_id=85780130&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle', 'The Indians made starter Danny Salazar''s addition to the 25-man roster official on Tuesday, and reliever C.C. Lee was optioned to Triple-A Columbus as a result.', 1, 1406076608, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 20:50:08 EDT\n	', 7),
(903, 'Asdrubal day to day due to back issue', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140722&content_id=85772392&notebook_id=85777878&vkey=notebook_cle&c_id=cle', 'Indians manager Terry Francona described Asdrubal Cabrera''s lower back as locked up on Tuesday, the night after Cabrera suffered spasms in the second inning of a 4-3 loss.', 1, 1406075898, 'Tue, 22 Jul 2014 20:38:18 EDT\n	', 7),
(904, 'Mariners get Morales back from Twins', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/mariners-acquire-kendrys-morales-from-twins?ymd=20140724&content_id=86096364&vkey=news_mlb', 'The Mariners acquired first baseman/designated hitter Kendrys Morales from the Minnesota Twins on Thursday in exchange for right-handed relief pitcher Stephen Pryor.', 1, 1406227309, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 14:41:49 EDT\n	', 0),
(905, 'Cashman prioritizes adding bat before August', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140724&content_id=86092510&notebook_id=86093544&vkey=notebook_nyy&c_id=nyy', 'The reformulated Yankees rotation has performed better than Brian Cashman would have anticipated, and the general manager said that he''d prefer to focus his attention on acquiring a big bat as the July 31 non-waiver Trade Deadline approaches.', 1, 1406224795, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:59:55 EDT\n	', 0),
(906, 'Tanaka feeling only marginal improvement', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140724&content_id=86092510&notebook_id=86093150&vkey=notebook_nyy&c_id=nyy', 'Masahiro Tanaka is still reporting discomfort in his right elbow, 10 days after receiving a platelet-rich plasma injection, but the Yankees are still hopeful to have the right-hander return to the big league mound this season.', 1, 1406224555, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:55:55 EDT\n	', 0),
(907, 'With Teixeira still hobbled, DL stint possible', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140724&content_id=86092510&notebook_id=86092576&vkey=notebook_nyy&c_id=nyy', 'Manager Joe Girardi said that the Yankees will likely make a roster decision regarding injured first baseman Mark Teixeira by Friday. Thursday''s series finale against the Rangers was the fourth consecutive game out of the starting lineup for Teixeira, who has a mild strain of his lower left lat.', 1, 1406223721, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:42:01 EDT\n	', 0),
(908, 'O''s acquire Minor Leaguer Paredes from Royals', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/os-acquire-minor-leaguer-jimmy-paredes-from-kc?ymd=20140724&content_id=86091310&vkey=news_mlb', 'The Orioles acquired Jimmy Paredes from the Royals for cash considerations on Thursday, and the utility man has been optioned to Baltimore''s Triple-A Norfolk affiliate.', 1, 1406222917, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:28:37 EDT\n	', 0),
(909, 'Rangers hope Feliz can cling to closer role', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140724&content_id=86088734&notebook_id=86089962&vkey=notebook_tex&c_id=tex', 'Rangers reliever Neftali Feliz is back in his role as closer. The right-hander still has to earn the job if he wants to keep it beyond this season.', 1, 1406222110, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:15:10 EDT\n	', 0),
(910, 'Texas cautious in scratching Tepesch Friday', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140724&content_id=86088734&notebook_id=86089850&vkey=notebook_tex&c_id=tex', 'The Rangers have scratched right-hander Nick Tepesch from Friday''s start against the Athletics as a precaution. Tepesch was needed in relief during Tuesday night''s 2-1 loss in 14 innings, and the club decided not to pitch him on short rest.', 1, 1406221989, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:13:09 EDT\n	', 0),
