(912, 'Tigers not counting on help from Hanrahan', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article/mlb/tigers-not-counting-on-help-from-joel-hanrahan?ymd=20140724&content_id=86088632&vkey=news_mlb', 'Joel Hanrahan signed with the Tigers in May, less than a year after undergoing Tommy John surgery, and team president/GM Dave Dombrowski said Thursday the club isn''t counting on the veteran right-hander to return the big leagues this year.', 1, 1406221429, 'Thu, 24 Jul 2014 13:03:49 EDT\n	', 0),
