(972, 'After pitching duel, mishap at plate stings Sox', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_23_kcamlb_chamlb_1&mode=recap_home&c_id=cws', 'An error on catcher Tyler Flowers during a ninth-inning play at the plate gave the Royals a 2-1 victory over the White Sox Wednesday afternoon at U.S. Cellular Field. Jose Quintana and his counterpart, James Shields, both gave up one run in seven innings.', 1, 1406156259, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 18:57:39 EDT\n	', 6),
(973, 'Sox turn to Noesi to open four-game set in Minnesota', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/mlb/gameday/index.jsp?gid=2014_07_24_chamlb_minmlb_1&mode=preview&vkey=preview_web_away&c_id=cws', 'When the White Sox last faced the Twins in June, the South Siders were swept away in four games during a rough eight-game losing streak. Both clubs will clash once again on Thursday night in the opener of another four-game meeting at Target Field, with Chicago turning an eye towards vaulting itself back into the division race.', 1, 1406150154, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 17:15:54 EDT\n	', 6),
(974, 'Top Sox pick Rodon debuts in Rookie League', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85919516&notebook_id=85919438&vkey=notebook_cws&c_id=cws', 'Carlos Rodon''s professional debut Tuesday night for the Arizona Rookie League White Sox featured one run allowed on two hits over one inning, and Chicago''s top pick in the 2014 First-Year Player Draft struck out one.', 1, 1406139186, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 14:13:06 EDT\n	', 6),
(975, 'Sox remember Buehrle''s perfecto on anniversary', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85919516&notebook_id=85919238&vkey=notebook_cws&c_id=cws', 'Mark Buehrle''s perfect game at U.S. Cellular Field against the Rays on July 23, 2009, is termed by White Sox play-by-play television announcer Ken "Hawk" Harrelson as his all-time favorite game. Harrelson contributed the famous "Alexei &#8230; Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! Yes! History!" call on Jason Bartlett''s grounder to shortstop Alexei Ramirez for out No. 27.', 1, 1406139185, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 14:13:05 EDT\n	', 6),
(976, 'Flowers makes it for son''s birth just in time', 'http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140723&content_id=85919516&notebook_id=85919436&vkey=notebook_cws&c_id=cws', 'A better-rested Tyler Flowers explained the scenario that took him from U.S. Cellular Field Monday night to Northwestern Memorial Hospital in time to be with his wife, Nancy, for the birth of their second child and first son.', 1, 1406139168, 'Wed, 23 Jul 2014 14:12:48 EDT\n	', 6),
